abstract: Morgan Pressel takes second place in second round of Evian Championship with six-under-par 65.
lead_paragraph: Morgan Pressel moved one shot behind the leader, Mi Hyang Lee, in the second round of the Evian Championship in Haute-Savoie, France.

headline.main: Pressel in Hunt at Evian Championship
